OL,4,Caunt living in care home
OL,6,FA man from Wiltshire stole #600k from
OL,7,Fhis aunt by abusing his position as
OL,8,Fpower of attorney.
OL,10,FA report was made to Wiltshire Police
OL,11,Fin September 2020 when payments to a
OL,12,Fwoman's care home kept bouncing. When
OL,13,Fthis was checked, it was found there
OL,14,Fwas no money in her bank account.
OL,16,FAfter an investigation, it was found
OL,17,Fthat the woman's nephew, David
OL,18,FEggleton, 71 and of Newbury Avenue in
OL,19,FCalne, had moved more than #600,000
OL,20,Finto his own account.
