OL,4,Caunt living in care home
OL,6,F"Throughout the case Eggleton claimed
OL,7,Fhis victim loaned and gifted him the
OL,8,Fmoney, even pointing to a loan
OL,9,Fagreement he had created allegedly
OL,10,Fwith her assistance, but during the
OL,11,Ftrial he admitted that the loan
OL,12,Fagreement was fraudulently created.
OL,13,FThis will of no doubt had a huge
OL,14,Fimpact on Lilian's wellbeing.
OL,16,F"We would urge anyone who sees
OL,17,Fsomething suspicious or has concerns
OL,18,Ffor someone to get in contact with us
OL,19,Fstraight away. You can do this on our
OL,20,Fwebsite, by calling 101 or 999 in an
OL,21,Femergency."
